sometimes its so hard to sleep in these sheets
where so much love has been made, then lost. 
i just roll around in regretful reminiscence for hours 

remind me to stop falling so hard. every time.
because i dont think i will ever shake that
"something missing" feeling
and i dont think i will ever stop pushing away
 people that i really love
and i am hurting, trying to say goodbye to so much

lately i just want to scream, 
and keep screaming 
until my voice doesnt exist 
and all i can do i sleep, and keep sleeping. 

i dont know who i am or what im doing or where im going 
or why i feel so fucking alone sometimes after the sun sets. 

but my broken heart is sad and pathetic in comparison 
to this planets real problems.
so i will focus on those and forget about me for a while. 

--____--

i dont like to sleep at night
i feel alive at night
all alone 
with no one to explain myself to
or force interaction with.

drives me nuts how much is driven by cost/

something feels just not quite right. 
i keep feeling like a change in scenery is the fix.
but i know that is ignorant and only quick.
i know the problem lies much deeper...
thats the problem..

"we can never obtain peace in the outer world 
until we make peace with ourselves"
tenzin gyatso

my soul and ego are at war..
i dont know who i am anymore. 
but have i ever?
does anyone ever?

passing my days, lost and longing..
i havent felt awake or even alive
in too, too long.
somebody wake me the fuck up! thanx.
